      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Oracle XStream CDC Source (Confluent JMX → Prometheus)\n\nRequires **JMX exporter** on Kafka Connect with `monitoring/jmx/kafka-connect.yml` (includes `debezium.confluent.oracle:*` and `kafka.producer:*`). **Restart Connect** after updating the JMX config. **topic.prefix** in the connector maps to label **`server`** in Debezium MBeans. If lag is negative or wrong, set **`database.os.timezone`** per [connector monitoring](https://docs.confluent.io/kafka-connectors/oracle-xstream-cdc-source/current/connector-monitoring-metrics.html)."
      },
      "title": "About",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "axisPlacement": "auto" },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 10,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "debezium_oracle_connector_total_number_of_events_seen{job=~\"kafka-connect\",context=\"streaming\"}",
          "legendFormat": "streaming {{server}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Total number of events seen (streaming)",
      "description": "MBean context=streaming — TotalNumberOfEventsSeen",
      "type": "timeseries"
